query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(an ci it lt ml n pi t) */ select min(n.name) AS cast_member_name,
min(pi.info) AS cast_member_info
from person_info AS pi
inner join aka_name AS an
on pi.person_id = an.person_id AND pi.note IS NOT NULL AND an.name IS NOT NULL AND ( an.name like '%a%' OR an.name like 'A%')
inner join info_type AS it
on it.id = pi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'mini biography'
inner join cast_info AS ci
on pi.person_id = ci.person_id AND an.person_id = ci.person_id
inner join name AS n
on n.id = pi.person_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = n.id AND n.name_pcode_cf BETWEEN 'A' AND 'F' AND ( n.gender = 'm' OR ( n.gender = 'f' AND n.name like 'A%'))
inner join movie_link AS ml
on ci.movie_id = ml.linked_movie_id
inner join link_type AS lt
on lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link IN ('references',
'referenced in',
'features',
'featured in')
inner join title AS t
on ml.linked_movie_id = t.id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1980 AND 2010;
